      • getUtilities

        public java.util.List<Tuple<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double>> getUtilities()
        Specified by:
        getUtilities in interface StandardInfo
        Returns:
        tuples [agent, utility] for all the ActionWithBids that were done, in that order (0 being the first action with a bid, etc). Agent is the party that did the action. Utility is the non-discounted utility of his offer. All utilities are in the utility space of the agent receiving this info.
